		<h1 class="entry-title">Italian Christmas Cookies</h1>		<img width="1000" height="667" src="https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Italian-Christmas-Cookies.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Italian-Christmas-Cookies.jpg 1000w, https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Italian-Christmas-Cookies-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Italian-Christmas-Cookies-900x600.jpg 900w, https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Italian-Christmas-Cookies-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Italian-Christmas-Cookies-390x260.jpg 390w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" />	
