	<div id="recipe-189161-notes" class="wprm-recipe-notes-container wprm-block-text-normal"><h3 class="wprm-recipe-header wprm-recipe-notes-header wprm-block-text-bold wprm-align-left wprm-header-decoration-none" style="">Notes</h3><div class="wprm-recipe-notes"><span style="display: block;">•	Do not overmix the dough.<br />
•	Chill dough if it feels sticky.<br />
•	Bake until lightly golden, not dark.<br />
•	Let cookies cool before glazing.<br />
•	Add sprinkles while glaze is still wet.</span></div></div>
