		</section><section id="text-23" class="widget widget_text"><div class="widget-title-right-bar">Meet Corrie</div>			<div class="textwidget"><div class="welcome-box"><img width="500" height="500" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-192 perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;500&#039;%20height=&#039;500&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20500%20500&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Corrie Duffy" data-src="https://www.corriecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/corrigan-duffy-headshot.jpg" /> Welcome to Corrie Cooks!<br />
I'm Corrie, and I have a deep love for all things food. If you're looking for some quick and easy recipes that are big on flavor, you've come to the right place! <a href="https://www.corriecooks.com/about/">Read more</a></div>
</div>
